title: Leverage Visio Online in your SharePoint Site and as a Teams App using SharePoint SFPx Framework
sortTitle: leverage visio online in your sharepoint site and as a teams app using sharepoint sfpx framework
description:
In this session we will show you how to use Visio Online to display Visio content in a SharePoint Site. Extraction of information from diagram and Customized Drill down capability will be demonstrated as an example of powerful online usage of Visio and SharePoint. You will learn how to build a React SPFx SharePoint WebPart with a Microsoft Visio component and make it also available in Teams :
-	Creation of an SPFx React Webpart using Yeoman Generator 
-	Adding a React Visio Component using Visio Javascript API
-	Deploying the solution to a tenant and to Teams.
